{"tid":1894141,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"(武肺文宣戰) 點解應上網扮支那人出盡奶力批鬥人地支援得武漢唔夠力&道德綁架","createTime":"2020-02-23T17:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T14:04:04.000Z","uid":4322,"like":91,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"1550fbf6350ac8a71eab942ce2f728d346ce7b94","tid":1894141,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"眼見咁多人會不惜氣力批鬥同路人唔夠黃咁撚有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捐得少又屌, 唔上前又屌, 咩都屌一餐, 道德標準直上天際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你不如出盡奶力扮支那人批鬥名人支持不足好過喇!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n咩意思? 首先開左個扮支那人既fb/ig/youtube/twitter acct (用殘體呀記住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>即係你要批鬥愛国名人唔夠愛国唔夠訓身支持道德綁架佢地!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>用苦行用聖人標準去批鬥對家!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1) <ins><strong>班明星好鍾意作歌拍片隔空支持</strong></ins><br />\n留言質問唱歌/打氣可以幫到咩手? 病毒會消失嗎? 武漢係需要人和物資!<br />\n當地醫護佢地有話要唱歌同打氣咩?!!! 我睇你只係愛人民幣不是愛国! <br />\n可以入去張學友 Jacky Cheung &ndash;《等風雨經過》MV玩下<br />\n［武漢肺炎］華語樂壇最強維穩武器：張學友 + 周杰倫出動了<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893935\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893935</a><br />\n2) <strong><ins>名人捐錢捐物資時要質問佢咁有錢點解唔捐多D! </ins></strong><br />\ne.g 捐一百萬咁少? 你咁有錢點解唔捐夠一千萬? 一千萬可以買多好多物資!<br />\n你拍一套電影都唔止一千萬! 難道你就唔可以為同胞奉獻嗎?!<br />\n捐一萬個口罩?! 你唔捐十萬個?!<br />\n捐普通口罩就問佢點解唔捐n95<br />\n3) <strong><ins>個班淨係口講支持中国!支持武漢!就質問佢點解唔捐錢!</ins></strong><br />\n佢話無錢就佢點解唔親身上去支持! 佢地缺人! 國難當前! 匹夫有責!<br />\n我要邀請你一齊去為佢地打氣! <br />\n4) <strong><ins>見到名人吃喝玩樂就質問國難當前點解可以仲有心情玩?!</ins></strong><br />\n你有無人性?! 同胞仲受緊苦! 知唔知當中使費可以幫到幾多武漢醫護!!??<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">參考文章: 日本社運失敗的歷史 (立場) <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Vh6cI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Vh6cI8&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=ddbe3bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Vh6cI8</a><br />\n//作者提醒抗爭者，當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調「苦行」，社運人士無論是自己或同路人的要求太高，也不讓人抗爭容下一點輕鬆，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂。如此思考方法，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥，失去了主流社會支持的死胡同。//</span><br />\n<br />\n成本: 零<br />\n效果: 將對家支持武漢既成本大大提高, 要不斷提升個標準<br />\n我要班名人明星再無心機去支持! 要佢地灰心! <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌你當成件事好似chur9同路人唔夠黃咁囉仆街! 道德綁架呀! 連登仔一定識喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n意想不到效果: 等真心藍絲一齊屌埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7feb0e23385043e053488da0e9f038cd59e9cf1d","tid":1894141,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"Pishh"},{"pid":"16cc27698173bad40cb517d1f7c0d379607202f4","tid":1894141,"uid":4322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:29:38.000Z","msg":"pishhh"},{"pid":"ff00984dfe8d339cc6bb169e0c56b89832e322a6","tid":1894141,"uid":154892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:31:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b25e5001a0c1d3bbd442c6899f5c58b50c0e2416","tid":1894141,"uid":154892,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"