ulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=ddbe3bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Vh6cI8</a><br />\n//作者提醒抗爭者，當年日本社運的致命傷，就是過度強調「苦行」，社運人士無論是自己或同路人的要求太高，也不讓人抗爭容下一點輕鬆，不容忍抗爭者可以有一絲快樂。如此思考方法，讓日本社運走入互相批鬥，失去了主流社會支持的死胡同。//</span><br />\n<br />\n成本: 零<br />\n效果: 將對家支持武漢既成本大大提高, 要不斷提升個標準<br />\n我要班名人明星再無心機去支持! 要佢地灰心! <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>屌你當成件事好似chur9同路人唔夠黃咁囉仆街! 道德綁架呀! 連登仔一定識喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n意想不到效果: 等真心藍絲一齊屌埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"應該係扮到好紅<br />\n不停屌d 大陸人唔肯認命為國家大局犧牲 之類<br />\n<br />\n咁佢地就會反感"},{"pid":"8f715a61016547c09883c1fdfb0578687eccc721","tid":1894141,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:46:56.000Z","msg":"推 好計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［黃色新聞圈］香港人 肯 撐 良 心 傳 媒 未，肯唔好扼殺佢地未<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893867\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893867</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3548749ca5049a85ef8a21d237e5e798606031ed","tid":1894141,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0dc547af7c434a6158ca6e1dedb2b416eb43bf2","tid":1894141,"uid":169195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1550fbf6350ac8a71eab942ce2f728d346ce7b94","tid":1894141,"uid":4322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"眼見咁多人會不惜氣力批鬥同路人唔夠黃咁撚有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n捐得少又屌, 唔上前又屌, 咩都屌一餐, 道德標準直上天際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><stron